179904.name: Share of global cumulative CO2 emissions from gas
179904.description: Cumulative production-based emissions of carbon dioxide (CO2) from gas since the first year of data availability, measured as a percentage of global cumulative production-based emissions of CO2 from gas since the first year of data availability. This is based on territorial emissions, which do not account for emissions embedded in traded goods. Each country's share of global CO2 emissions from gas has been calculated by Our World in Data using global CO2 emissions from gas provided in the Global Carbon Budget dataset. Global gas emissions include all country emissions.
